onbuttonblack1Action() - Method in class com.example.resistrontest.resistronController
In the method below we declare the 1st button of line 1 named buttonblack1 button + its color "Black" + "line number", all the buttons are named in this way, then the color of this one is repeated at the beginning of the line on the label, moreover the color of the button is also repeated on the diagram of the resistance, at the ring level concerned, finally we declare its value and link it to the "Display();' method, which calculates the value of the resistance, and allows the display of the unit and its tolerance.
